♫ <i>Oh, oh, oh　Yeah!</i> ♫

156
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:50,750
♫ <i>Oh, oh, oh</i> ♫

157
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:53,550
♫ <i>Oh, oh, oh　Yeah!</i> ♫

158
